Thanks for riding the Korean Content Wave! The KOCOWA team has worked hard on making sure you get upgrades like faster video and limited interruptions. So to provide you a better experience the KOCOWA app will only support iOS 11 and higher. There will be no service disruptions to enjoy these perks. Your subscription stays the same but you ll get an even better experience. Be the first to take advantage of new features which will be added regularly.
